Jobs are sold to graduates in SA - A list of government officials reveled and nation shocked Selling Jobs in South Africa Graduates are unemployed and job seeking with no luck. Most have been to endless interviews with zero luck. The reason behind all that has been exposed. Jobs these days come with a price tag. Speaking to over ten unemployed graduates they confirm that they have lost out on Job opportunities because they do not have deep pockets. 8/10 graduates say that they have had people approaching them on job opportunities with a price tag. This is just why the rich gets richer and the poor gets poorer. Rich kids don't qualifications all they need is the right amount to secure jobs they don't even need